preference.name: CAE_structuremap_log_content_scope
preference.preference_description: Defines the scope of the CAE Structure Map log content. The value is leveraged by the "CAE_persist_StructureMapLog" preference, and persisted within the dataset identified by the "CAE_structuremap_log_dataset_name" preference. Valid values are "Summary" (default value) and "Detailed".
